OL,3,CKiller jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cpartner in 'savage attack'
OL,6,FA 32-year-old man has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto 18 years in prison for murdering
OL,8,Fhis partner in a "sustained and
OL,9,Fsavage" attack.
OL,11,FCorey Dryden repeatedly struck 31-year-
OL,12,Fold Megan Hughes on the head and body
OL,13,Fwith a knife and claw hammer at her
OL,14,Fhome in Chirnside, in the Scottish
OL,15,FBorders, in the early hours of 9
OL,16,FFebruary this year.
OL,18,FThe mother-of-two was stabbed 27 times.
