OL,4,Cpartner in 'savage attack'
OL,6,FAt about 2.15am, the couple's next-
OL,7,Fdoor neighbour was woken by the sound
OL,8,Fof a disturbance, and heard Ms Hughes
OL,9,Frepeatedly shouting for help and
OL,10,FDryden telling her to "shut up,"
OL,11,Freports PA.
OL,13,FDryden dialled 999 at about 4.35am,
OL,14,Fbut when paramedics arrived Ms Hughes
OL,15,Fhad died.
OL,17,FAccording to PA, the 32-year-old
OL,18,Finitially claimed Ms Hughes had
OL,19,Fattacked him and that he had acted in
OL,20,Fself-defence, but on 27 June he
OL,21,Fadmitted murder.
OL,26,@rD@WOU
