OL,3,CKiller jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cpartner in 'savage attack'
OL,6,FHe was sentenced at the High Court in
OL,7,FEdinburgh on Thursday (24 July).
OL,9,FSentencing Dryden, judge Lord Harrower
OL,10,Fsaid: "In the early hours of Sunday 9
OL,11,FFebruary you carried out a sustained
OL,12,Fand savage attack using a large
OL,13,Fkitchen knife and a claw hammer."
OL,15,FHe said Ms Hughes had sustained stab
OL,16,Fwounds to the front and back of her
OL,17,Fchest, face, neck and left arm, and
OL,18,F"blunt force trauma" the front and
OL,19,Fback of her head.
