OL,3,CKiller jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cpartner in 'savage attack'
OL,6,FHe added: "Ms Hughes also sustained
OL,7,Fdefence-type injuries to her left
OL,8,Fthumb and left wrist, indicating that
OL,9,Fshe remained conscious and aware of
OL,10,Fwhat was happening during at least
OL,11,Fpart of the attack."
OL,13,FThe judge told Dryden his actions had
OL,14,Fcaused "terrible devastation" to Ms
OL,15,FHughes's entire family.
OL,17,F"Such was the nature of the injuries
OL,18,Fyou inflicted, they were deprived of
OL,19,Fthe opportunity to look at her face
OL,20,Fone last time," the judge told him.
