OL,3,CKiller jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cpartner in 'savage attack'
OL,6,F"No sentence of this court can
OL,7,Falleviate their anguish."
OL,9,FThe judge also recounted an incident
OL,10,Fin a pub on September last year, just
OL,11,Ffive months before the fatal attack,
OL,12,Fwhich saw police called.
OL,14,F"When they arrived they witnessed you
OL,15,Fshouting and swearing at Ms Hughes,
OL,16,Fcalling her derogatory names," he said.
OL,18,FHe went on: "Ms Hughes had expressed a
OL,19,Ffear that you would kill her if she
OL,20,Freturned home that night.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@YO]vD@AOUxD@^O]zD@MOU
