OL,3,CKiller jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cpartner in 'savage attack'
OL,6,F"Ultimately those fears were realised."
OL,8,FLord Harrower sentenced Dryden to life
OL,9,Fwith a minimum term of 18 years in
OL,10,Fprison, saying "the only sentence for
OL,11,Fthe crime of murder is life
OL,12,Fimprisonment".
OL,14,FDryden, who attended the hearing by
OL,15,Fvideolink from prison dressed in a red
OL,16,Fjumper, showed no emotion as he was
OL,17,Fsentenced.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@gO]rD@POUtD@MO]
