OL,3,CKiller jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cpartner in 'savage attack'
OL,6,F"I will never be about to forgive
OL,7,Fmyself, or accept the pain I have
OL,8,Fcaused."
OL,10,FShe added Dryden has little memory of
OL,11,Fwhat happened on the night of the
OL,12,Fattack, saying he had been under the
OL,13,Finfluence of drugs and alcohol and
OL,14,Fthat it had been a "blur".
