OL,6,FCommenting after the sentencing, Moira
OL,7,FOrr, who leads on homicide and major
OL,8,Fcrime for the Crown Office and
OL,9,FProcurator Fiscal Service, said:
OL,10,F"Corey Dryden is a violent and
OL,11,Fdangerous man who murdered Megan
OL,12,FHughes in her home, where she had the
OL,13,Fright to be safe.
OL,15,F"After subjecting her to a horrific
OL,16,Fassault, he left his partner on the
OL,17,Ffloor to die instead of calling for
OL,18,Fhelp.
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@AOU
