OL,3,CKiller jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cpartner in 'savage attack'
OL,6,F"His cruel and callous actions have
OL,7,Frobbed Megan of her future and left
OL,8,Fher family and loved ones to deal with
OL,9,Fthis unimaginable loss. Our thoughts
OL,10,Fremain with them.
OL,12,F"Dryden has now been held accountable
OL,13,Ffollowing this prosecution, which
OL,14,Fshould send a clear message to
OL,15,Fperpetrators of domestic abuse."
OL,17,FPolice Scotland Detective Chief
OL,18,FInspector Laura White said: "This was
OL,19,Fa vicious and calculated attack by
OL,20,FDryden that tragically resulted in
OL,21,FMegan's death.
